      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(proxy): apply enhanced NO_PROXY matching to global undici dispatcher",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nWhen \\`HTTPS_PROXY\\` is set in the environment, \\`ensureGlobalUndiciEnvProxyDispatcher()\\` installs a global undici \\`EnvHttpProxyAgent\\` that routes ALL HTTP requests through the proxy — including internal plugin requests that should bypass it.\n\nThe built-in undici \\`EnvHttpProxyAgent\\` NO_PROXY matcher does not support:\n- **Leading-dot subdomain patterns** like \\`.myqcloud.com\\` (matches \\`foo.myqcloud.com\\`)\n- **CIDR notation** like \\`100.64.0.0/10\\`\n- **Octet wildcards** like \\`100.64.*\\`\n\nOpenClaw already has an enhanced \\`matchesNoProxy()\\` function in \\`proxy-env.ts\\` that supports all of these, but it was only used by \\`shouldUseEnvHttpProxyForUrl()\\` for provider HTTP helpers — NOT by the global dispatcher.\n\n**Impact**: qqbot plugin COS chunked uploads fail with \"fetch failed\" in proxy environments, making image sending completely non-functional.\n\n## Solution\n\nWrap the global \\`EnvHttpProxyAgent\\` with a \\`createNoProxyAwareEnvDispatcher()\\` proxy that checks \\`shouldUseEnvHttpProxyForUrl()\\` — which uses OpenClaw's enhanced \\`matchesNoProxy()\\` — before routing each request.\n\nRequests matching NO_PROXY (with full subdomain/CIDR/wildcard support) are routed through a direct \\`Agent\\` instead of the proxy.\n\n### Before\n\\`\\`\\`\nensureGlobalUndiciEnvProxyDispatcher()\n  → setGlobalDispatcher(EnvHttpProxyAgent)  ← undici NO_PROXY only\n  → qqbot COS PUT → proxy → \"fetch failed\"\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n### After\n\\`\\`\\`\nensureGlobalUndiciEnvProxyDispatcher()\n  → setGlobalDispatcher(NoProxyAwareEnvDispatcher(EnvHttpProxyAgent))\n  → each dispatch checks shouldUseEnvHttpProxyForUrl()\n  → qqbot COS PUT → matchesNoProxy(\".myqcloud.com\") → bypasses proxy → success\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n## Evidence\n\n### Test matrix\n\n| Test file | Tests | Result |\n|-----------|-------|--------|\n| \\`undici-global-dispatcher.test.ts\\` | 33 | ✅ Passed |\n| \\`proxy-env.test.ts\\` | 55 | ✅ Passed |\n| \\`undici-runtime.test.ts\\` | 5 | ✅ Passed |\n\n**Total**: 93 tests passed across all affected modules.\n\n### Formatting\n\\`oxfmt --check\\`: ✅ Passed\n\n### Diff summary\n\\`\\`\\`\n1 file changed, 57 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n### Root cause\nhttps://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/a13e2b92b3/src/infra/net/undici-global-dispatcher.ts#L291-L296\n",
